column5: Anybody out today or Saturday? What was the walking like? PM if you prefer.
I bet not very nice with all that snow, lol.
Ya, that's what I was wondering about. Last week before the snow it was just getting thick.
i was there friday and ice is about 7" solid black iced.. caught a laker too

At Shanty Bay today. Few fish caught & none by me. About 6" of solid ice with 4" of snow cover and slushy in spots. The walk out in the morning was harder than the walk back. By then some of the trails where packed down somewhat.
